reviewText: This is an old story about romance. I enjoyed it on my iPad. Im very glad that Amazon had a hard copy available, however I think it would been have been very nice if they had an electronic version that I could download
Fast service....awesome!!!!  Excellent peruvian production,nice DVD to my Latin Collection in perfect condition... Totally New!!! Thanks for this awesome service!!

si te gusta Vanesa Terkes entonces usted debe tener esta pelcula. La base es, hay un escritor de canciones que no pueden poner sus pensamientos en el papel hasta que se encuentra con ella, al chocar con su ciclomotor, ella es su musa y le inspira a la grandeza. ver las pruebas y tribulaciones y de tragedis curso a lo largo del camino.
